{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/blog/2020-10-14/styled-components-add-media-query","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"sunny.w","author":"sunny wang"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"63eba375-734e-5d06-85c7-3d12eae894b4","excerpt":"Media query 在下的使用，和普通 css 下是一样的，只是 styled-components 支持 SCSS 的语法\n，另外可以在 es6 的模板字符串(tagged template)下有独特的写法。  传统的写法 styled-components 下的写法 styled-component 下的 scss 写法  后面接的是 模板字符串，可以插值(interpolate…","html":"<p>Media query 在<code class=\"language-text\">styled-components</code>下的使用，和普通 css 下是一样的，只是 styled-components 支持 SCSS 的语法\n，另外可以在 es6 的模板字符串(tagged template)下有独特的写法。</p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/styled-comp-scss.jpeg\"></p>\n<h2>传统的写法</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">#wrapper {\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: row;\n  @media (max-width: 768px) {\n    flex-direction: column;\n  }\n}</code></pre></div>\n<h2>styled-components 下的写法</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> styled <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"styled-components\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> Wrapper <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> styled<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>div<span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: row;\n  @media (max-width: 768px) {\n    flex-direction: column;\n  }\n</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>styled-component 下的 scss 写法</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> Article <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> styled<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>div<span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">\n  > h3 {\n    margin-bottom: 1rem;\n    > a {\n      text-decoration: none;\n    }\n  }\n  \n  .snapshots{\n    display: flex;\n    \n    > img {\n      @media (min-width: 1024px} {\n        width: 30%;        \n      }\n    }\n  }\n</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">styled.div</code> 后面接的是 模板字符串，可以插值(interpolate)，所以可以把不同分辨率的配置抽出来：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">// config/device-size.js</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> size <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  mobile<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"425px\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  tablet<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"768px\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  desktop<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"1024px\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> device <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  mobile<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">(max-width: </span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>size<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>mobile<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">)</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  tablet<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">(min-width: </span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>size<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>tablet<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">) and (max-width: </span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>size<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>desktop<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">)</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  desktop<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">(min-width: </span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>size<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>desktop<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">)</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>最终的 styled-components media query 写法</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> Article <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">styled</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Card<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">\n  > h3 {\n    margin-bottom: 1rem;\n    > a {\n      text-decoration: none;\n    }\n  }\n\n  .snapshots {\n    display: flex;\n\n    > img {\n      @media </span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>device<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>desktop<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\"> {\n        width: 30%;\n      }\n    }\n  }\n</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"styled-components add media query","date":"October 14, 2020","description":"如何在styled-components下使用media query来做响应式设计","tags":["react","styled-component"]}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2020-10-14/styled-components-add-media-query","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2020-10-14/js-wasm-fibonacci-compare"},"frontmatter":{"title":"javascript vs webassembly fibonacci benchmark"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/2020-10-13/gatsby-add-pagination"},"frontmatter":{"title":"gatsby page add pagination"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["1824009237","63159454","636771615"]}